{"tid":498739,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【沈大師現象】燈！全部都係燈！","createTime":"2017-12-14T05:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T02:21:44.000Z","uid":29314,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1e40e15d4a4f2992cdd7cd9e77923e5d94d31be0","tid":498739,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"早係四十幾年前，已經有本書*講，投資市場無先知（guru），所謂投資專家選股，同搵隻馬騮掟飛鏢落報紙既證券報價版去揀股無分別。<br />\n<br />\n2017年，有三個學者發表左一份研究報告**，佢地統計左六十八個forecasters 係1998年至2012年，針對S&amp;P 500指數所作既6,627項預測，有以下發現：<br />\n<br />\n# 呢批預測平均命中率係48%。（仲衰過掟銀仔擲公字）<br />\n<br />\n# 只有6% ，即係四個，命中率達70%-79%。<br />\n<br />\n# 只有三分一既投資專家，命中率高過50%。<br />\n<br />\n# 有40%專家命中率係40%-50%。（不如我擲公字啦！）<br />\n<br />\n# 有3%係明燈，命中率低過20%。（沈大師D friend黎）<br />\n<br />\n# AFAM Capital Asset Management既CIO，John Buckingham 係今次研究裡面命中率最高，達78%<br />\n<br />\n無論1973年既投資經典、定2017年既學術研究，都指出「投資世界無先知」呢個道理。睇完以上數據之後，你仲信郭蛋治、肥青、鄧猩猩、前瑞銀陸生、&hellip;&hellip;？識得揀，梗係信沈大師啦！買佢對家嘛！<br />\n<br />\n註：<br />\n<br />\n* &quot;A Random Walk Down Wall Street&quot; (1973), by Burton Malkiel<br />\n<br />\n**伸延閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=2944853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D2944853&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=979127d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=2944853</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同步連載，岩睇既請like and share<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWestRiceGoo&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=27c58532\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwestricegoo&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=f2de8c2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo</a>"},{"pid":"8e5e49c2f9bb00cac10c75aaefc0cc807a8ab7e0","tid":498739,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/150344_7431d20e646acb704f3e7b87e04697aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F150344_7431d20e646acb704f3e7b87e04697aa.png&h=f1900035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f8b4a404032cae9eed035dcbab2c8bbcc60d400","tid":498739,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687da63a8f10e1361e829913693c1c65e488b6f3","tid":498739,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大C"},{"pid":"7c417434ecc0f9a97f1cf54802886c984cf8fc25","tid":498739,"uid":11258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/150344_7431d20e646acb704f3e7b87e04697aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F150344_7431d20e646acb704f3e7b87e04697aa.png&h=f1900035&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9edc1a463d995703f99dfdaeb9c69980fd4654","tid":498739,"uid":33712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:47:32.000Z","msg":"咁牙擦遲下又審判大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f7afc407b04f0115c4a88a066c8ce623868429","tid":498739,"uid":7760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"可以完全唔準都唔係咁易"},{"pid":"18777b0da0e